{"tid":230565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味，香港起條跑道既成本，夠起悉尼嗰新機場五次","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T12:37:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e247e0b326d2464eae6665ada907818a4ac0cd04","tid":230565,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"消息傳來，悉尼將興建第二機場，造價50億澳元（註1），相當於港幣300億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n悉尼第二機場構想圖 （來源：<a href=\"http://abc.net.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fabc.net.au&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=b2578b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">abc.net.au</a>）<br />\n悉尼選擇在西面的新地點興建第二機場，而不是在原有機場加建一條跑道，因為這樣才會不受空域限制，百分百發揮新機場的航班運轉容量，同時又創造出新的發展地理空間，能夠帶動一系列連鎖效益，反觀香港建第三條跑道，空域飽和，毫無效益可言，完全沒有第二機場的好處，是一個笨選擇。<br />\n<br />\n第三條跑道已公布的造價是一千四百多億元，是悉尼第二機場造價的五倍左右，但是早有消息透露，第三條跑道的造價已知超過二千億元（註2），更是悉尼第二機場造價的七倍！一條跑道對整個機場，價錢五比一，甚或七比一，反差之大，無以名之！第三條跑道的「貴」，十分突出，相對於悉尼的「慳神」，機管局是全香港最大的「大嘥鬼」。<br />\n<br />\n看到這個對比，硬要在不適當地方興建受飽和空域包圍的第三條跑道的愚不可及，是否明顯得很？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註1     香港電台  2017年5月2日  「悉尼將建第二機場 造價達50億澳元」  <a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1328213-20170502.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1328213-20170502.htm&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=dbebd2a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1328213-20170502.htm&h=4dbc9aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1328213-20170502.htm</a><br />\n註2     信報  2014年6月17日  「機場第三跑道預算傳激增50%」  <a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/113922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F113922&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=9f8d6090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/113922</a>"},{"pid":"9f0953503a2a50ec344117c5b7e7fd7229ff1732","tid":230565,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tiandiyouqing.blogspot.hk/2017/05/blog-post.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiandiyouqing.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F05%2Fblog-post.html%3Fm%3D1&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=6fcd924c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tiandiyouqing.blogspot.hk/2017/05/blog-post.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"eafca9dea91685ae1b529a75ea3f84defe56ee2d","tid":230565,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"港豬：香港人工材料全世界最貴 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔見港豬人工最高"},{"pid":"c5526e9b3336c48e6cb1217d58a96740a423eac1","tid":230565,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬：香港人工材料全世界最貴 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過唔見港豬人工最高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔撚見我人工高鬼佬五倍，屌佢屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}